OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1778217983
OL,3,CMurder accused told Ian Watkins 'have
OL,4,Ca good sleep' after stabbing, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FA prisoner accused of murdering
OL,8,Fpaedophile Lostprophets singer Ian
OL,9,FWatkins told him "have a good night's
OL,10,Fsleep" after stabbing him and then
OL,11,Fboasted that he would be "famous", a
OL,12,Fcourt has heard.
OL,14,FRico Gedel, 25, is one of two men
OL,15,Fcharged with murdering the disgraced
OL,16,Frock star at HMP Wakefield, where
OL,17,FWatkins was serving 29 years for child
OL,18,Fsex offences.
OL,20,FGedel and his co-defendant Samuel
OL,21,FDodswort, 43, both deny the charges.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/15
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
