OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1778217983
OL,3,CMurder accused told Ian Watkins 'have
OL,4,Ca good sleep' after stabbing, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FOn the opening day of their trial at
OL,8,FLeeds Crown Court, the jury heard
OL,9,FWatkins was attacked in his cell at
OL,10,Fthe high-security prison.
OL,12,FProsecutors said Gedel went into the
OL,13,Fcell after it was unlocked on 11
OL,14,FOctober last year and stabbed him
OL,15,Fthree times in the head and neck with
OL,16,Fa home-made knife.
OL,18,FGedel then handed the weapon to
OL,19,FDodsworth, who disposed of it in a bin.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/15
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1778217983
OL,3,CMurder accused told Ian Watkins 'have
OL,4,Ca good sleep' after stabbing, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FProsecutor Tom Storey KC said that as
OL,8,Fprison officers ran to take hold of
OL,9,FGedel, he "stood there, holding his
OL,10,Farms outstretched and offering no
OL,11,Fresistance to them whatsoever".
OL,13,FAs he passed Watkins' open door he
OL,14,Fthen said: "Have a good night's sleep,
OL,15,FWatkins lad."
OL,17,FMr Storey said staff who were told to
OL,18,Fobserve Gedel through the hatch in his
OL,19,Fcell door commented on "his perky
OL,20,Fdemeanour".
OL,26,@qD@KOUsD@^O]{D@XOU|D@JO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/15
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1778217983
OL,3,CMurder accused told Ian Watkins 'have
OL,4,Ca good sleep' after stabbing, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,F"He discussed with one of them the
OL,8,Foffence that had led to him being
OL,9,Fimprisoned at HMP Wakefield in the
OL,10,Ffirst place, and he said something to
OL,11,Fthe effect of 'If I'm going to do life
OL,12,Ffor murder, I'm going to make sure
OL,13,Fit's worth it'," the prosecutor said.
OL,15,F"He also told the same officer, 'If
OL,16,FI've killed him, you could be talking
OL,17,Fto someone famous'."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@PO]wD@AOUyD@TO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/15
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1778217983
OL,3,CMurder accused told Ian Watkins 'have
OL,4,Ca good sleep' after stabbing, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FHe later told police that he was
OL,8,Fjealous of "nonce prisoners" because
OL,9,Fthey "got treated like royalty," and
OL,10,Fthat he thought it was disgusting
OL,11,Fhaving to share a wing with sex
OL,12,Foffenders at HMP Wakefield, where they
OL,13,Fwere not segregated.
OL,15,FThe jury was told it was "a joint
OL,16,Foffence" between the two defendants,
OL,17,Fand Dodsworth knew it was going to
OL,18,Fhappen.
OL,26,@pD@LOUpD@\O]qD@FOUqD@`O]wD@ZOUxD@HO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/15
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1778217983
OL,3,CMurder accused told Ian Watkins 'have
OL,4,Ca good sleep' after stabbing, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FMr Storey KC said Watkins, who was a
OL,8,F"particularly notorious and high-
OL,9,Fprofile" prisoner, received two notes
OL,10,Fthe day before he was killed which
OL,11,Faccused him of getting another
OL,12,Fprisoner kicked off the wing, demanded
OL,13,Fmoney from him and threatened violence.
OL,15,FHe said that, although it was unclear
OL,16,Fwhether these notes lay behind the
OL,17,Fattack, prisons are places where
OL,18,F"grudges are borne, and acted upon...
OL,19,Fand where 'grassing' or 'snitching' on
OL,20,Fothers is viewed in a poor light".
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@HO]zD@AOU|D@aO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/15
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1778217983
OL,3,CMurder accused told Ian Watkins 'have
OL,4,Ca good sleep' after stabbing, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe court heard Gedel had been moved
OL,8,Finto the same wing as Watkins and
OL,9,FDodsworth the day before the attack,
OL,10,Fand "coincidentally" put in the cell
OL,11,Fnext to Watkins.
OL,13,FOn the morning of Watkins' death,
OL,14,Fprison officers started unlocking the
OL,15,Fcells on B wing after 9am, and Gedel
OL,16,Fleft his cell, but Watkins chose to
OL,17,Fremain inside.
OL,26,@rD@EOUrD@TO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/15
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1778217983
OL,3,CMurder accused told Ian Watkins 'have
OL,4,Ca good sleep' after stabbing, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe court heard Gedel and Dodsworth
OL,8,Fmet in another prisoner's cell, and
OL,9,Fthat Dodsworth entered the cell with a
OL,10,F"dressing gown or towel wrapped up in
OL,11,Fa bundle" before leaving without it.
OL,13,FAfter talking to Dodsworth and another
OL,14,Finmate, Gedel briefly went back into
OL,15,Fhis own cell and then stood leaning
OL,16,Fagainst the railings, while Dodsworth
OL,17,F"loitered" near the top of the stairs
OL,18,Fand appeared to be acting as a
OL,19,F"lookout", jurors heard.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@IO]yD@AOUyD@JO]{D@AOU{D@IO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/15
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1778217983
OL,3,CMurder accused told Ian Watkins 'have
OL,4,Ca good sleep' after stabbing, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FMr Storey said: "At this time Gedel
OL,8,Fwas, in all likelihood, waiting for a
OL,9,Fmoment when the prison officers on the
OL,10,Flanding were out of sight, and when he
OL,11,Fwould have an opportunity to carry out
OL,12,Fthe planned attack on Mr Watkins."
OL,14,FCCTV showed Gedel going into Watkins'
OL,15,Fcell just before 9.20am and leaving
OL,16,Fjust 20 seconds later, before walking
OL,17,Ftowards Dodsworth and passing him
OL,18,Fsomething.
OL,26,@oD@QOUtD@bO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/15
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
